{"tid":1387993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過點解d狗越黎越癲?","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T16:13:47.000Z","uid":293123,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f5753e4a9c1c1b1b670ea6bb1546789c664efdb3","tid":1387993,"uid":293123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:38:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得係因為好多輿論都係批評d狗, 尤其元朗單野之後, 連其他紀律部隊同政府部門都表態, 依家就搵d平民黎發泄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n經過27号同28号, 大家都見到d狗唔係想驅散d平民, 係想現場圍打同圍捕d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 同埋到各主要車站抄身分證搜身拘捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n既然佢地因輿論而生壓力, 應該繼續各地幫佢地宣揚, 等佢地壓力爆煲, 好過一直同班狗硬碰硬, 大家be water留有用之軀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"7acf6356f419feab6f23c5419ba4b675e853f91f","tid":1387993,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:39:22.000Z","msg":"對得住前線！對得住義士！<br />\n一日政府無回應 一日都要繼續抗爭！<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n堅持五大訴求！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝 衝出困局<br />\n形象似義勇軍<span style=\"color: violet;\">(crusade)</span>般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通?<span style=\"color: violet;\">(訴求？)</span><br />\n如戴著面具<span style=\"color: violet;\">(mask)</span>去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<span style=\"color: violet;\">(不屈？)</span><br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<span style=\"color: violet;\">(憤怒？)</span><br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷著理想那怕痛<span style=\"color: violet;\">(revolution)</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfDAuxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfDAuxC.png&h=60385d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnOwNja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnOwNja.png&h=f5b7bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9ad0527e21daa72f933b1c7f0083d86b3610834a","tid":1387993,"uid":264083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n号<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb37aaddb82f910af8c6424ff96f0e01236bc99","tid":1387993,"uid":208253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"号你老母"},{"pid":"428824b136635040c9c33df41faf4badd8039dd9","tid":1387993,"uid":74593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:12:41.000Z","msg":"号？號？"},{"pid":"d31c73d34b62bc0640ba19de5081efd4bd656d92","tid":1387993,"uid":274934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"借個位黎擺擺 <br />\n入黎簽左佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入黎簽左佢 斷popo武器<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388013</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e715fce5791fec4566d902f8358915b30b56dec4","tid":1387993,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:13:47.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點，西灣河東區法院，聲援義士。"}]}